@notice Executes the bundled transaction:
1. Transfers tokenIn via Permit2.
2. Swaps tokenIn to cbBTC.
3. Approves and deposits cbBTC into RiftExchange.
@param amountIn The amount of tokenIn to swap.
@param swapCalldata The calldata for the swap.
@param params The DepositLiquidityParams for RiftExchange.
@param owner The token owner's address.
@param permit The PermitTransferFrom data.
@param signature The permit signature.
@return cbBTCReceived The amount of cbBTC received.

@notice Transfers tokens using Permit2.
@param amountIn The amount to transfer.
@param permitted The PermitTransferFrom data.
@param signature The permit signature.

@notice Executes the swap and returns the received cbBTC.
@param swapCalldata The calldata for the swap.
@return cbBTCReceived The amount of cbBTC received.

@notice Approves and deposits cbBTC into RiftExchange.
@param params The DepositLiquidityParams for RiftExchange.
@param cbBTCReceived The amount of cbBTC to deposit.

@title Bundler
@notice Bundles an ERC20 → cbBTC swap with a deposit into RiftExchange.
Uses Permit2 for token approvals.
